Class ChoresAllocation

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.ChoresAllocation
  • public class ChoresAllocation
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is responsible for creating a ChoresAllocation object. The object uses the TreeMap data structure to store a Chore object and an ArrayList[String].
